<section id="about">
    <h2>About Brija Kairouan</h2>
    <p>
        The Kairouan dialect has unique pronunciation, vocabulary, and expressions
        that distinguish it from other Tunisian regions.
    </p>
</section>

<section id="culture">
    <h2>Culture & Traditions</h2>
    <p>
        Kairouan is famous for its religious heritage, traditional food, poetry,
        carpets, and strong cultural values passed from generation to generation.
    </p>
</section>

